nnels in scandinavia bulgaria and the baltic countries typically the portfolio structure for these channels is one primary channel tv nova and then secondary channels tv tv diema etc these channels generate primarily advertising revenues and are classified as freetv but a majority of the scandinavian freetv channels are encrypted and subject to decoding fees networks channel type sweden norway denmark estonia latvia lithuania bulgaria  general tv sweden tv norway tv denmark tv estonia free tv latvia tv lithuania free nova television free general secondary tv sweden free viasat  tv denmark tv estonia lnt tv lithuania free diema supplementary tv tv tv sport hd tv norway tv puls tv sport  tv sport  tv estonia tv latvia tv latvia kanāls  tv lithuania free diema family kino nova nova sport diema sport diema sport  pay televisionedit subscription tv services paytvedit mtg operates the viasat satellite platform in the scandinavia and baltic states offering both inhouse and third party channels the sports channels available in the different scandinavian countries differ somewhat depending on different rights held for different markets and different business agreements mtg also operates viaplay an online paytv service in the nordic countries mtg is also present in the mcn space through its part ownership of splay the largest swedish mcn multi channel network on youtube and zoomintv one of the largest mcns that has local presence in  countries and produces short form videos in  markets worldwideedit the trace platform is also available in the worldwide with the following channels trace urban sdhd trace tropical sdhd trace africa sdhd trace toca sdhd trace mziki sdhd trace naija sdhd trace gospel sdhd trace sport stars sdhd scandinaviaedit the following channels are available in all scandinavian countries viasat film premiere sdhd viasat film action sdhd viasat film family viasat film comedy sdhd viasat film hits viasat series sdhd esportstv hd viasat golf sdhd except denmark 